snippet.title: Best VGM 1299 - Nora to Toki no Koubou - The Pure Aroma at the Herbalist
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1058 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ung2q_BVXWY

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Nora to Toki no Koubou Kiri no Mori no Majo (2011)
The Pure Aroma at the Herbalist
Michiko Naruke
